      • isReadOnlySubobjectRoot

        public boolean isReadOnlySubobjectRoot()
        If true than this entity can only be included/excluded AND none of its children can be updated in any way. This means that during a commit we won't attempt to commit any of its children.
        Returns:
        true if this entity is only include/exclude AND all child entities are display-only.
